        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-376761874" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-376761874" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="376761874">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/haidb/">haidb</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2011-04-10</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">汪曾祺的散文恬淡，但不算清新；满仓满谷，但作料很少；“嘈嘈切切错杂弹”；汪老说自己随遇而安大概算是准确的，“文如其人”用在他身上也相当站得住脚。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="540689857">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
