                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/qinxinsandie/"> _Traissic_</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-06-05</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">还是这种气定神闲的生活小品对我的胃口，讲讲吃吃喝喝玩玩旧事，很羡慕那个时期的学生生活。虽说那个年代也有很多艰苦，但看文字始终充满了正面的能量和生活的热情，让人看了心情舒畅。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="617038738">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-617038738" class="vote-count">3</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-617038738" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="617038738">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Clytze.vs.rose/">阿梦</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-12-17</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">多是旧时看过的文章</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="921336640">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-921336640" class="vote-count">4</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-921336640" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="921336640">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/viking7117/">撒旦的表妹</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-05-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">这本算是合集吧，除了人间草木、五味，后面还有讲西南联大、沈从文、父亲、祖父的，文字都很“疏朗清淡”，但读来却很有感觉，沈从文去世那段看湿眼眶。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="502054286">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-502054286" class="vote-count">82</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-502054286" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="502054286">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/flowermumu/">欢乐分裂</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-02-29</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">静思往事，如在目底，心闲气静，至浓则至淡，此身虽在总堪惊。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

